Interface RequestHeaders

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HttpHeaders, HttpObject, Iterable<Map.Entry<AsciiString,​String>>
    public interface RequestHeaders
extends HttpHeaders
    Immutable HTTP/2 headers for an HttpRequest.
